value.string: Ocean front at its best for whale watching and views of the Island of Molokai. Quiet location at the end of the cul de sac. Near Pool and within walking distance to Kapalua Bay Beach. 3 pools and two tennis courts for further enhancing the Bay Villa life style experience. Great location. Nice conservation area in front with path to the rocks below where the turtles come in to feed. Great ocean view.

Rolling fields of green, untouched soil and breath taking ocean/mountain views tucked away and preserved in NATURAL beauty is a special place referred to as KOU. This property offers numerous buildable sites with unobstructed bi-coastal view and includes a PRIVATE shoreline hideaway. Offered together with a shoreline parcel, this is a unique and very special part of OLD HAWAII. Please allow 4-5 hours for a complete viewing opportunity. 2 parcels included in this listing which includes Tmk# 2-1-7-04-07 and 2-1-7-04-08.
